
"You can't tell me that your crying for nothing. What's wrong"? He asked kissing my neck making me relax.
"I can't finish the Script tonight and its giving me a headache"
"Well of course not you started two days ago" He said confused.
"But it usually takes me about three days to write" I said as his petite hands moved from my waist to my stomach.
"Yeah, but your pregnant witch means you get stressed easily meaning you should take a break from writing"
I look at him with wide eyes.
"Only until the pregnancy is over"
I sigh but nodded my hands going over his ones witch were on my stomach.
"That's our baby".
I giggle and rest against him.
"Mmmh"
